        <item>
            <title>香港科技園公司與 UBS 展開合作提供展示平台　連接初創與潛在客戶「説好香港科研故事」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/03/ubs-cooperate-with-hkstp-provide-showcase-platform/people-interview/ppl_interview/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ubs-cooperate-with-hkstp-provide-showcase-platform</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/03/ubs-cooperate-with-hkstp-provide-showcase-platform/people-interview/ppl_interview/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 09:29:53 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人物專訪]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[業界專訪]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[HKSTP]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[UBS]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[香港科技園公司]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1208813</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近年社會一直在説「説好香港故事」，而在科研上，大家平常可能在新聞一直看到外國甚麼甚麼企業又成功研發哪種哪種新技術，其實在香港亦有不少初創企業一直在默默耕耘，在各領域研發不同的新科技以改善人類社會。UBS 日前就宣佈與香港科技園公司（科技園公司）展開合作，希望藉著旗下的數碼中心，將香港建構成為真正的世界科研中心。</p><h2>初創需要「轉折」以求成功</h2><p>在發佈會中，科技園公司行政總裁黃克強就表示，在世上 70% 的初創企業都是失敗收場，而如果他們要成功，他們需要有人提供「關鍵轉折（Pivot）」的協助，令他們將研發出來的技術，「扭一扭」做出更符合市場需求的產品，令成品可以商品化並賺取利潤。今次與 UBS 瑞銀的合作，就是希望可以幫助剩餘的 30% 初創達至成功。而瑞銀財富管理亞洲區主席兼瑞銀香港區主管及行政總裁盧彩雲亦表示，在這次與科技園公司的合作中，他們會提供旗下位於尖沙咀的數碼中心（The Digital Hub），讓科技園公司的初創企業展示他們的科研成果，UBS 則會充當超級連繫人（Super Connector）的角色，將初創科技企業與企業家、學術人員、策略性合作伙伴及投資者連結在一起。透過這次合作，UBS 及科技園公司希望可以為科技園公司旗下的科企提供更好的培育環境，令這些科企的成品「可落地」，甚至可為初創公司提供一站式服務，例如：與瑞銀投行合作為初創公司籌組上市，最終令香港成為其中一個擁有世界科研中心的城市。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07555-1.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208816 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07555-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07555-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07555-1-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07555-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07555-1-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07555-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲UBS 瑞銀日前與科技園公司舉行聯合發佈會，宣佈將會展開合作，為科技園公司旗下初創企業提供展示平台，希望可連接初創與潛在客戶，而當日亦有不少科技園公司初創企業參與。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07420.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208817 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07420-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07420-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07420-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07420-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07420-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07420.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲科技園公司行政總裁黃克強在發佈會中表示，初創要成功一定要有人或機構提供「關鍵轉折（Pivot）」協助，令他們將研發出來的技術，「扭一扭」做出更符合市場需求的產品，令成品可以商品化並賺取利潤，這亦是今次他們與 UBS 合作希望達到的成果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1211090 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/403405541_1467492680484888_4049132474191661816_n-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/403405541_1467492680484888_4049132474191661816_n-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/403405541_1467492680484888_4049132474191661816_n-506x900.jpg 506w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/403405541_1467492680484888_4049132474191661816_n-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/403405541_1467492680484888_4049132474191661816_n-864x1536.jpg 864w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/403405541_1467492680484888_4049132474191661816_n.jpg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲瑞銀財富管理亞洲區主席兼瑞銀香港區主管及行政總裁盧彩雲亦表示，在今次合作中，UBS 會充當超級連繫人（Super Connector）的角色，將初創科技企業與企業家、學術人員、策略性合作伙伴及投資者連結在一起。UBS 及科技園公司希望透過這次合作，可以為科技園公司旗下的科企提供更好的培育環境，令這些科企的成品「可落地」。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07514-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208841 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07514-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07514-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07514-1-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07514-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07514-1-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07514-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲UBS 旗下的數碼中心（The Digital Hub）設有一塊極大的展示牆，初創企業在向潛在客戶展示產品時可以善加利用。</p><h2>多間初創分享研發成果　不少已商品化解決市場需要</h2><p>而在發佈會當日，科技園公司就邀請了多間落戶在科技園公司的本地初創企業，趁機分享他們的研發成果，當中不少更加入了近年大熱的人工智能（AI）元素，例如：有迎合近年大眾注重衞生而設的便攜版遠紫外光滅菌器及智能通風管淨化器、用於快速瞭解客戶脫髮問題的儀器、30 秒一掃即可初步瞭解身體健康狀況的裝置、由布料出發為消費者帶來更舒適兼有實際用效的服裝、甚至為長期痛病患者提供根治方案的醫療用產品亦有。當中不少更已商品化並已推出市場，例如：推出智能通風管淨化器的企業 LR IOT 就表示已內置在不少由市建局重建的新樓宇、提供 30 秒一掃瞭解身體狀況的 Panoptic AI 公司更已將產品應用在不少私營醫院，他們的 CEO 及創辦人黃君朗更表示此產品正等待獲得 FDA 認證，未來更會與其他機構，例如：保險公司推廣此產品，更有可能會推展至位於大灣區或東南亞的機構。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07470.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208820 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07470-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07470-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07470-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07470-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07470-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07470.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07477.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208821 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07477-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07477-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07477-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07477-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07477-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07477.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07478.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208822 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07478-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07478-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07478-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07478-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07478-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07478.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在發佈會當中，有不少初創企業亦有展示他們的科研成果，例如：上圖這款由 Panoptic AI 公司研發的裝置 Vitals，就可以使用平板或擁有鏡頭的裝置，只需短短 30 秒就可透過掃描用家面部皮下的血液流動提取生理數據，之後就會在短時間提供全面的初步健康分析報告。他們的 CEO 兼創辦人黃君朗表示 Vitals 正等待 FDA 認證，而現在已獲多間本地私營醫院採用。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208823 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558-3-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558-3-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07558-3.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07557.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208824 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07557-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07557-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07557-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07557-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07557-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07557.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而另一間展示成品的企業 Dr.Rock，他們的總經理王建鎮就展示了他們為長期痛症患者設計，內含獨特中國天熱稀土（紅砭石）及石墨烯的產品，據王氏表示紅砭石會發出對身體就有效的遠紅外線，可與細胞產生同頻共震，有助活化細胞、促進血液循環、放鬆肌肉及恢復體能，更對舒緩及根治痛症很有幫助。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07395.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208835 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07395-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07395-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07395-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07395-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07395-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07395.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07399.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208825 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07399-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07399-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07399-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07399-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07399-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07399.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07400.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208826 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07400-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07400-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07400-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07400-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07400-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07400.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而他們的產品不只有美容槍、按摩槍，溫陽百變墊專業板更可創造適當的磁場環境，幫助人體自癒。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07567.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208827 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07567-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07567-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07567-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07567-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07567-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07567.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07562.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208828 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07562-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07562-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07562-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07562-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07562-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07562.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另一間名為 Comfiknit 亦在現場展出採用獨特布料的衣服，他們最新研發出這款擁有保濕功能的布料，可將一定程度的水氣保留在皮膚上，對於舒緩困擾不少港人的濕疹有很大幫助，穿著乘搭飛機亦十分舒服。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07569.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208829 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07569-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07569-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07569-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07569-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07569-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07569.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07571.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208830 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07571-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07571-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07571-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07571-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07571-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07571.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另一間展示研發成果的本地初創 LR IOT，他們現場就展示了這款獲市建局贊助開發的 UV-C VentGuard 智能通風管淨化器，可以有效切斷天井傳播鏈，為家居提供更安心及衞生的環境，而這成品已獲市建局安裝於旗下不少重建項目，可説已成功「落地」。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07572.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208831 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07572-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07572-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07572-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07572-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07572-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07572.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲LR IOT 亦表示他們下一步將會為建築業研發為高空工作工人而設的安全設備，萬一有工人未有穿戴合適防護工具，中央管理平台就會收到警告，方便建築公司及時提醒工人要繫好安全帶，最大程度避免悲劇發生。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07444.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208832 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07444-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07444-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07444-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07444-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07444-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07444.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07375.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208833 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07375-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07375-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07375-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07375-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07375-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07375.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而這件由 ERGO 222 展出的 XOne 222 納米遠紫外光滅菌器，就可以在短時間為用家進行消毒，可有效殺滅 99.9% 冠狀病毒，而且體積細小，充滿一次電亦可使用 4 小時，確實十分實用。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07457.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208836 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07457-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07457-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07457-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07457-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07457-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07457.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07463.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1208837 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07463-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07463-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07463-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07463-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07463-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/DSC07463.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲此外，相信大家也十分熟悉的本地頭髮護理企業「髮再生」（HairCoSys）亦有展示他們的 AI 護髮方案，可以短時間為客戶進行 AI 頭髮頭皮分析，再透過 AI 進行產品服務配對，希望為用家找出最佳的頭髮護理方案。</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/03/ubs-cooperate-with-hkstp-provide-showcase-platform/people-interview/ppl_interview/">香港科技園公司與 UBS 展開合作提供展示平台　連接初創與潛在客戶「説好香港科研故事」</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
